data.description: Beautiful Brick Ranch in the heart of downtown Columbia on just under an acre!  The property has 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, an oversized Island, an open-concept kitchen and living room, walk in pantry and a screened-in porch with open brick patio and carport! Downtown where nature is meshed together on a beautiful lot with travel convenience to both shopping and Bi-pass! Equity is possible in every direction with this property. The main bedroom has a working wood-burning fireplace. The secondary has a private on-suit bathroom as well as a walk-in shower. The property has beautiful mature trees,  and a block storage building. Roof and appliances are 4 years old.  Seller needs 25 days after closing.
